tz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/two-al-jazeera-journalists-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-gaza/00000191-122a-d015-adf7-fa3ea7000000</link><description>半岛电视台阿拉伯语记者伊斯梅尔·阿尔·古尔和他的同事、摄影师拉米·阿尔·里菲星期三在哈马斯政治领袖伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚在加沙的家附近的沙蒂难民营进行报道后被杀，哈马斯当天早上在德黑兰被杀。据半岛电视台报道，他们的汽车成为以色列国防军的目标</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 09:15:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/two-al-jazeera-journalists-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-gaza/00000191-122a-d015-adf7-fa3ea7000000</guid></item><item><title>我如何发现自己陷入了定居者大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-i-found-myself-inside-a-settler-pogrom/00000191-0eb0-dba6-a59d-0efb03b80000</link><description>在参与寻找一名在约旦河西岸失踪的以色列青少年的过程中，我亲身体验了无处可去的血腥现实</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 03:23:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-i-found-myself-inside-a-settler-pogrom/00000191-0eb0-dba6-a59d-0efb03b80000</guid></item><item><title>哈尼亚遇刺事件明确表明：以色列人质问题并非内塔尼亚胡议程的重中之重</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/haniyehs-assassination-made-it-clear-israeli-hostages-are-not-top-of-netanyahus-agenda/00000191-0f51-dba6-a59d-0f5b3e970000</link><description>尽管存在升级的危险，哈马斯政治局局长被杀还是提高了以色列总理的地位。他可以用它来罢免国防部长加兰特，后者支持一项包括开火的协议</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 03:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/haniyehs-assassination-made-it-clear-israeli-hostages-are-not-top-of-netanyahus-agenda/00000191-0f51-dba6-a59d-0f5b3e970000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡遇刺庆祝活动结束后，以色列将不得不为此买单</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-will-have-to-pick-up-the-tab-after-netanyahus-assassination-celebrations/00000191-0f50-dba6-a59d-0f5ba6ff0000</link><description>哈马斯和真主党高级官员被杀的第二天，地区战争的可能性变得更大，人质交易面临受挫的危险——至少目前是这样。 